import React from 'react';
import {Form, Col, Row, Button} from 'react-bootstrap'
import './ProvaRicerca.css'

function ProvaRicerca(){
    return(
        <Form className="BarraRicerca">
            <Form.Row>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridEmail">
                <Form.Label>Dove?</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control type="name" placeholder="Inserire la città dove si vuole andare" />
                </Form.Group>

                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridPassword">
                <Form.Label>Check-in</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control type="date" placeholder="Inserire cognome cliente" />
                </Form.Group>

                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridAddress1">
                    <Form.Label>Check-out</Form.Label>
                    <Form.Control type="date" placeholder="Inserire indirizzo cliente"/>
                </Form.Group>

                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridState">
                <Form.Label>Ospiti</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control as="select" placeholder="Inserire numero ospiti">
                    <option></option>
                    <option value="US">1</option>
                    <option value="CA">2</option>
                    <option value="AF">3</option>
                    <option value="AL">4</option>
                    <option value="DZ">5</option>
                    <option value="AS">6</option>
                    <option value="AD">7</option>
                    <option value="AO">8</option>
                    <option value="AI">9</option>
                    <option value="AQ">10</option>
                </Form.Control>
                </Form.Group> 

                <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
                    Invia dati
                </Button>
            </Form.Row>

        </Form>
    );
}
export default ProvaRicerca;
